strings:
<voice_0x010010D6><se_high>Carrie: I hate you, Cash!
I SO cannot stand you!

<voice_0x010010D7><se_high>Carrie: We're both orphans, remember!?
Dad took us in when we were still babies!

<voice_0x010010D8><se_high>Carrie: That means we don't know who's actually older!
For all you know I could be your older sister!
<voice_0x010010D9><se_def>Cash: Yeah, and for all I know maybe you're actually a boy! Whatever, Carrie. Why don't you just chill out? I'm giving you an equal chance!

<voice_0x010010DA><se_def>Cash: Like, how many times do we have to go over
this? We do the contest. The winner inherits
the Golding family's fortune. End of story.
<voice_0x010010DC><se_def>Cash: You're too scared to go to the Dragon Graveyard, even with your bodyguards.
<voice_0x010010DD><se_high>Carrie: As if! Don't be more of a jerk than usual, Cash.
<voice_0x010010DE><se_high>Carrie: Huh!? Cash, we have guests! They could be applying for the bodyguard position!

<voice_0x010010DF><se_def>Cash: Hello, there! Please forgive our manners.
Welcome to the Golding mansion!
